description: Cucina Bambina is making Miami mouths water with the power of their gourmet Italian cuisine.Sandwiches, pastas, burrata, and even desserts, this truck can do it all. If there's something you want for your next big event that they don't serve, then they're happy to accommodate you as best they can.Do you love your mobile meals to be made with fresh ingredients, superb skill, and lots of love? Then look no further than Cucina Bambina!
name: Cucina Bambina
